# Naming (new files)

Full pack: [docs/product/NAMING.md](docs/product/NAMING.md).

| Kind | Convention |
|------|------------|
| React components | `PascalCase.tsx` |
| Hooks / modules / mounts / contracts | `camelCase.ts(x)` |
| Screen folders | kebab **`=` `screenId`** (`book-step-1`, not `book-step1`) |
| Page / kit CSS | `kebab-case.css` (BEM block ≈ screenId) |
| Product doctrine docs | `SCREAMING_SNAKE.md` |
| Project docs | `docs/projects/<id>/…` |
| Scripts | `kebab-case.mjs` |
| Tests | `*.test.ts` in `__tests__/` (colocated OK for tiny UXDS pure units) |

**Hard forbid:** no new `proto*` / `Proto*` filenames — this is UX Studio (`studio*`, domain folders). Prefer `window.__studio*`; keep `__proto*` as legacy aliases. Do not half-rename `.proto-*` CSS / `data-proto-*` (phase 2).

**Forward-only:** do not mass-rename historical docs. High-ROI renames only when they stop agents stumbling (e.g. folder ≠ URL id).
